---

<section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-purple-900/20 to-gray-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(139,92,246,0.3) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Amazing Features
      </h2>
      <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-pink-400 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-300 mb-12 text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        This MOD Pack comes with lots of Features that will blow up Your mind. With these features, You can take Your Gameplay to The Next Level.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg text-center hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-6 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Customizable</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          The most interesting feature of This Mod is that it is a customizable mod. You can change her hair color, clothes, skin color, and many things you want. Cool, right?
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg text-center hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-6 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Easy to Use</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Jenny MOD is designed to be user-friendly and intuitive, making it easy for anyone to use regardless of their playing skill. Jenny will obey your instruction and help you to fill your desired dream full.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg text-center hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-6 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Purchasable Services</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Jenny provides various in-game services. It would be best if you had in-game currency to use these services. Using this currency you can do whatever you want with Jenny.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>